  
  Name:  hypot
 
  #include <math.h>
  float hypotf(float side1, float side2);
  double hypot(double side1, double side2);
  long double hypotl(long double side1, long double side2);

  The hypot( ) family of functions returns the length of the 
  hypotenuse given the lengths of the two opposing sides.
  That is,the functions return the square root of the sum of the 
  squares of side1 and side2.

  Related Function:  sqrt

